{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"false","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/false","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath 참고 문서</a></b>: <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 요소</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 함수</a>, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 축</a>\n</div><p></p>\n<p><br>\n <code>false</code> 함수는 boolean false를 반환합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ea.b5.ac.eb.ac.b8","title":"구문","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">false()\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.b0.98.ed.99.98","title":"반환","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Boolean <code>false</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a3.bc.ec.9d.98","title":"주의","isH3":true,"content":"<p>이 함수는 비교(comparison)하는 부분에 쓸모가 있습니다.</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">&lt;xsl:if test=\"boolean((1 &amp;gt; 2) = false())\"&gt;\n The expression evaluates as true\n&lt;/xsl:if&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a0.95.ec.9d.98","title":"정의","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-false\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.3</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_.ec.a7.80.ec.9b.90","title":"Gecko 지원","isH3":true,"content":"<p>지원함.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"false 함수는 boolean false를 반환합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"false","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"false","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"false","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"false","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/xpath/functions/false","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-cont